		----------------------------------------
		PLANE PARALLEL ISOTROPIC SCATTERING CODE
		----------------------------------------

This directory contains the source codes for the plane parallel, isotropic 
scattering code.  The code runs on SGI and SUN workstations and PCs running 
LINUX.  Unlike the 3D grid codes, the plane parallel code passes some 
arguments via COMMON blocks.

The FORTRAN files are:

	iarray.f  
	isoscatt.f  
	moments.f  
	newphot.f  
	output.f  
	planepar.f  
	ran2.f

Include files are:

	arrays.txt  
	blob.txt  
	random.txt

Input parameters are in:

	slab.par

The file that compiles the code and creates the executable file 'slab' is:

	Makefile


